# MK-OS VPS Hermes gateway resilience — deploy to /etc/cron.d/mkos-watchdog
# webhook-keeper: re-assert the webhook within <=60s of any restart-window drop (deterministic registration).
* * * * * root /opt/mkos-watchdog/webhook-keeper.sh >/dev/null 2>&1
# watchdog: behavioral health probe (real webhook delivery) + auto-recovery every 5 min.
*/5 * * * * root /opt/mkos-watchdog/telegram-watchdog.sh >/dev/null 2>&1
